{"tid":336168,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Lenovo正式發布模塊化旗艦Moto Z2 Force：Snapdragon 835+6GB RAM","createTime":"2017-07-26T07:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T12:14:50.000Z","uid":25125,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a68cac5d65cba7dfe6011e99c085049a5021e05","tid":336168,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:54:08.000Z","msg":"Lenovo正式發布模塊化旗艦Moto Z2 Force：Snapdragon 835+6GB RAM、360&deg;相機模組！<br />\nby ZingGadget   2017.07.26 12:31AM<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool3c.com/files/contentparty/mSu4UCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2Fcontentparty%2FmSu4UCx.jpg&h=377bea7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了手機外，Lenovo 也在發布會上正式宣布了一款全新的Moto Mod 模組！其中最令人矚目的就是之前所曝光的360&deg; 相機模組，售價是定在了299.99美元。<br />\n<br />\n2017-07-26 00:31:13 by Lim Jeff @ Zing Gadget [引用來源]<br />\n<br />\n今天，Lenovo 旗下的Motorola 品牌重磅新品終於和我們見面啦！本地時間11點晚上，Lenovo 就在紐約舉辦了一場新品發布會，主角當然就是模塊化旗艦手機Moto Z2 Force 啦！雖然手機名字和設計看起來都與Z2 Play 有點像，不過手機細節與配置方面還是有差的。不多說，直接來看手機！<br />\n<br />\nMoto Z2 Force 規格參數：<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool3c.com/files/contentparty/mSu4UCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2Fcontentparty%2FmSu4UCx.jpg&h=377bea7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 5.5寸1440p Quad HD Super AMOLED屏幕（Shattershield 不碎技術）<br />\n<br />\n- Snapdragon 835 八核處理器<br />\n<br />\n- 4/6GB RAM+64/128GB ROM 存儲組合<br />\n<br />\n- 前置500萬像素鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n- 後置雙1200萬像素鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n- 2730mAh 電池容量<br />\n<br />\n- 支援Turbo Charge 快充技術<br />\n<br />\n- 支援指紋識別<br />\n<br />\n- Android 7.1.1 系統<br />\n<br />\n- 黑、金、灰<br />\n<br />\n售價：750美元（約RM3211）(約港幣$5857)<br />\n<br />\n那轉到手機的外形，Z2 Force 是配備了一塊5.5寸的Quad HD AMOLED 屏幕，值得一提的是它也使用了Moto 獨有的ShatterShiled 技術，主要功能就是可以保證手機屏幕蓋板玻璃不會輕易跌碎。<br />\n<br />\n厚度方面其實也比上一代薄了不少，<span style=\"color: red;\">最薄處只有6.1mm</span>。但是這可是要付出代價的，也就是<span style=\"color: red;\">手機電池縮水變成了2730mAh</span>，但也好在用戶可以通過充電模塊補上這不足。不過這裏小編要提一提各位的是，Z2 Force 也支持了Turbo Charge 快充技術，多多少少都會解決用戶對手機續航能力的擔憂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool3c.com/files/contentparty/eWkOxGq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2Fcontentparty%2FeWkOxGq.jpg&h=04b1b7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了手機外，Lenovo 也在發布會上正式宣布了一款全新的Moto Mod 模組！其中最令人矚目的就是之前所曝光的360&deg; 相機模組，售價是定在了299.99美元（約RM1285）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool3c.com/files/contentparty/pBEYqyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2Fcontentparty%2FpBEYqyd.jpg&h=d676f9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nok，講完了所有發布會的所介紹的重點后，接著就是大家最想要知道的手機售價！據官方的揭曉，這款Moto Z2 Force 是會提供黑、金、灰三種配色，官方售價是定在了750美元（約RM3211），當地即日起可以預購，正式開賣日則是需要等到8月10日。<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/127078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F127078&d=KpYxcfbBRDrKVsFuHxlYx1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=dfa89682\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/127078</a><br />\n癮科技facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cool3c.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcool3c.tw&d=KpYxcfbBRDrKVsFuHxlYx1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=67ed64f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cool3c.tw</a>"},{"pid":"3fe09cd1f3b613ed4329f323537a554f6f0b8e1e","tid":336168,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"咁薄有撚用咩，我要大電呀"},{"pid":"b330ae19274b9f4550798714d97c3a8c21aaa42f","tid":336168,"uid":58863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"2730 電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11bc749f86a402c7d07670652cd2b9ba6af99c6","tid":336168,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想買"},{"pid":"750d169dcd050b9fb45c2bdca16c99874